  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nWhen preparing to mount a user's cryptohome, cryptohomed will unsafely recursively delete a directory in a chronos controlled path. A race condition exists to insert symbolic links which can result in the arbitrary deletion of files and directories across the filesystem."
